    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1895-08-18T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1895-08-18T00:00:00-05:00" n="534" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d534">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">
                        <persName type="from">Mavroyeni Bey</persName> to Mr.
                                    <persName type="to">Olney</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Translation.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Imperial Legation of Turkey</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1895-08-18">
                            <hi rend="italic">August 18,
                                1895</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Mr. <hi rend="smallcaps">Secretary of State</hi>: I have the honor to
                            confirm my note of yesterday’s date relative to the Tarsus incident.</p>
                <p>Owing to an error in the transmission of the Sublime Porte’s telegram, I
                            told your excellency that the quarrel had taken place between a cook
                            named Christi, who was the bearer of American papers, and a certain
                            Zeibek Ali. I should have said, “The quarrel took place between the cook
                            of Mr. Christie, an American citizen, and a certain Zéibek Ali.”</p>
                <p>I beg your excellency to take note of this correction.</p>
                <p>Be pleased to accept, etc.,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Mavroyeni.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
